3. `HIGH / code-bug` 阅卷接口把 `school_id` 直接信任为外部输入，学校级角色可以越权读写别的学校数据。`POST /grading/assignments` 用 `req.school_id or 当前学校`，`GET /grading/assignments`、`GET /grading/progress/{exam_id}`、`GET /grading/quality-report/{exam_id}` 也都允许 query 参数覆盖当前作用域，没有任何“只能等于 current_role.school_id”的校验。[assignment_router.py#L46](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py#L46) [assignment_router.py#L62](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py#L62) [assignment_router.py#L76](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py#L76) [quality_router.py#L24](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/quality_router.py#L24) 这和计划里反复强调的 school scope 相冲突，但测试只用了 `platform_admin`，没有覆盖学校级角色的越权路径。[test_grading_assignments.py#L42](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_api/test_grading_assignments.py#L42) [test_quality_checks.py#L5](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_api/test_quality_checks.py#L5)

